quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  79,1,“Ndikulumbilira (angelo) amene amazula mwamphamvu (mizimu ya osakhulupirira)
  79,2,“Ndikulumbiliranso (angelo) amene amachotsa moleza (mizimu ya okhulupirira)
  79,3,“Ndi omwe amasambira (nayo mizimuyo) mu mlengalenga (ponka nayo ku malo ake oyembekezera)
  79,4,“Ndi iwo amene akupikisana pokwaniritsa malamulo a Allah
  79,5,“Ndi iwo (angelo) amene akulongosola malamulo (Ake). (Ndithudi inu anthu mudzauka kwa akufa)
  79,6,"“Patsiku lomwe (lipenga loyamba lidzaimbidwa), dziko lapansi ndi mapiri ake zidzagwedezeka (ndipo aliyense adzafa)"
  79,7,“Ndipo kudzatsatira kuyimba kwa lipenga lachiwiri (kumene kudzaukitsa akufa onse)
  79,8,“Tsiku limenelo mitima idzanjenjemera ndi kuopa
  79,9,“Maso a eni mitimayo adzakhala ozyolika (chifukwa chamadandaulo)
  79,10,"“(Osakhulupirira) akunena: “Kodi nzoona tidzabwezedwa pambuyo pa imfa monga tidalili kale?”"
  79,11,““Pomwe ife titakhala mafupa ofumbwa (tingabwezedwe ndi kuukitsidwa mwa tsopano)?”
  79,12,"“Adanena (mokanira ndi mwachipongwe): “Choncho kubwerera kumeneko ngati kudzakhalepodi kudzakhala kotaika (ndi kopanda phindu kwa ife. Pomwe ife sindife oyenera kutaika).”"
  79,13,“(Musaganize kubwererako nchinthu chovuta). Ndithundithu Kiyamayo ndi nkuwo umodzi
  79,14,“Mwadzidzidzi (zolengedwa zonse) zidzangoona zili pa dziko latsopano (zili zamoyo)
  79,15,“Kodi yakufika (iwe Mtumiki) (s.a.w) nkhani ya Mûsa
  79,16,“Pamene Mbuye wake adamuitana pa chigwa choyera (chotchedwa) Tuwaa
  79,17,"“(Adamuuza kuti) pita kwa Farawo ndithu iye wapyola malire, (mkudzitukumula kwake ndikupondereza anthu)"
  79,18,"“Choncho ukamuuze kuti: “Kodi ukufuna kudziyeretsa?”"
  79,19,““Ndikuti ndikuongolere kwa Mbuye wako kuti uzimuopa?”
  79,20,“(Basi Mûsa) adamuonetsa (Farawo) chozizwitsa chachikulu
  79,21,“Koma (Farawo) adatsutsa (Mûsa pazimene adadza nazo zija) ndi kunyoza
  79,22,“Kenaka adabwerera uku akulimbika kutsutsana naye (Allah)
  79,23,“Adawasonkhanitsa (afiti) uku akuitana anthu
  79,24,"“Nanena: “Ine ndine mbuye wanu wapamwambamwamba!”"
  79,25,“Pamenepo Allah adamulanga chifukwa cha mawu ake omaliza ndi oyamba
  79,26,“Ndithu pa zimenezi pali phunziro (lalikulu) kwa yemwe akuopa Allah